Package common.FinalProjectAPI.chatroom

Contains interfaces for interacting with Chatrooms, including IChatroom (the actual chatroom object itself) and IMsgReceiver (the adapter that allows a user to communicate with a remote Chatroom object).

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IChatroom
    An interface that represents a single Chatroom object.
    ICmd2ModelAdapter
    Adapter used by the visitor pattern to send a message to the view.
    IMsgReceiver
    The interface that represents all adapters that handle communication between a remote user and the mini-MVC tied to a Chatroom object.
